4.5 million will be spent on patches in Pskov asphalt
04 Nov 2019, 20:41 by Alexey Gromov

In Pskov, they are urgently looking for a contractor for patching yards. 36 addresses should receive patches in the asphalt by December 13th. The budget of the company is 4.5 million.

The Pskov administration decided to patch the roads: until December 13, in the yards of 36 houses of Pskov, they plan to patch the pits. 4.5 million rubles were allocated for patches. Although we previously reported that the deputy governor refused the money that was allotted for repairs so as not to roll them in the snow. Below is a list of houses. whose residents can enjoy smooth roads in a month:

